- Fixed Windows Autopilot enrollments intermittently hanging on the Enrollment Status Page at "Account setup" until the 3-hour timeout. Fleet now keeps the enrollment in the ESP until the device acknowledges the user-scope release command with a success status, re-sending it each session (during OOBE the device rejects user-scope writes until its user MDM context initializes). This also prevents relaxing the device's MDM poll schedule while it is still on the Enrollment Status Page.
